   Dear Families,

 We hope you and your children are well and enjoying some time off this
summer. Last week, the Chancellor provided additional information about
fall 2020 school re-opening plans in this letter
<https://auth-infohub.nyced.org/docs/default-source/default-document-librar=
y/update-for-families-on-school-reopening.pdf>.
